text: Democrats struggle with who they are

subs.text: First, the Repubs are about the rich people from all over the world, sucking America like a ripe piece of fruit. In contrast, the Democrats are about Americans. The people of this country. All races including white. Women, rich and poor and middle.

What matters to Democrats is the health, happiness and success of Americans. We the people. Baseball, hot dogs and apple pie. Education. We are not scared of the future but we have to prepare for it, say the Democrats.
